    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just feeling overwhelmed. it's like... the person everyone knows is just a shell. i'm performing 24/7 and it's so exhausting. if there's nobody actually \"in here\" anymore, what's the point of keeping up the act? it feels like i'm just maintaining a lie for people who don't even know the real me.",
